WEBVTT

00:00:01.912 --> 00:00:03.237
Hauwajui.

00:00:04.150 --> 00:00:05.436
Hauwaoni.

00:00:06.405 --> 00:00:08.408
Lakini daima wapo wanazunguka,

00:00:09.404 --> 00:00:11.084
wananong'oneza,

00:00:11.108 --> 00:00:12.922
wakitengeneza mipango ya siri,

00:00:13.700 --> 00:00:17.382
wakijenga jeshi la mamilioni ya wanajeshi.

00:00:18.826 --> 00:00:20.617
Na wanapoamua kushambulia,

00:00:21.435 --> 00:00:23.697
wanashambulia kwa wakati mmoja.

00:00:27.130 --> 00:00:28.909
Ninaongelea kuhusu bakteria.

00:00:28.933 --> 00:00:30.258
(Kicheko)